    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你刚刚逃离了吞噬你家乡的混乱。格林舍这个孤立的山区小村庄的友好居民为你提供了一个新家。修复舒适的老农舍，照料田地。但要小心，瘟疫正在来临。社区必须齐心协力，才能让每个人生存下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238470/extras/bb8b2bc9eb41efa6724fa1365ee6c65e.poster.avif?t=1770583270\" width=600 height=86 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238470/extras/bb8b2bc9eb41efa6724fa1365ee6c65e.webm?t=1770583270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>喂养它们</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保持地窖储藏充足，平衡草食动物和肉食动物的需求。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过腌制、腌渍、晾干和熏制防止食物腐烂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >耕种作物田，种植果树和坚果树。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驯养野生动物，养殖以稳定供应鸡蛋、牛奶和肉类。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采集种子、花朵、草药、坚果、根和浆果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >去附近的沼泽、河流和湖泊钓鱼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成为社区的一员</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集材料，建造村庄项目以增强社区。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >捐赠标本用于研究，发现提高生存几率的新方法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与格林舍可爱的村民交朋友。但不要太依赖……可能不是每个人都会存活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索世界</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入格林舍山谷的矿井，挖掘每一条矿脉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验美丽的动态变化季节和天气。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用各种家具、围栏、铺路石装饰你的家和农场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238470/extras/e03ae545cbb74fb54344e6ed64a64b44.poster.avif?t=1770583270\" width=500 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238470/extras/e03ae545cbb74fb54344e6ed64a64b44.webm?t=1770583270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238470/extras/e03ae545cbb74fb54344e6ed64a64b44.mp4?t=1770583270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
